    "body": "The issue I see is that `balance` isn't a reserved keyword in solidity, so some contracts will contain a `balance` method.  For example, [iEarn](https://github.com/iearn-finance/itoken/blob/master/contracts/YDAI.sol#L506).\r\n\r\nWhat if we insated add an `address` member, that gives access to the object's address type?\r\n\r\n```python\r\npiggy: PiggyBank = PiggyBank(piggy_address)\r\nassert piggy.address.is_contract\r\nassert piggy.address.codehash == self.expected_piggy_codehash\r\n```",
